  "description": {
   "en": "Wonderful stories revolving around a pair of lovers and their friends.  \n  \n1) Kimi ni Sasayaku Mirai (The Future I Whisper to You)  \nKazuki-senpai has been reported to have been involved in a fatal airplane crash. But miraculously, he shows up on Renji's doorstep…  \n  \n2) Kimi ni Sasayaku Rakuen (The Paradise I Whisper to You)  \nContinuing the story of Kazuki and Renji - 16 years later.  \n  \n3) The Loneliness I Whisper to You  \nMore of Kazuki and Renji - 18 years later.  \n  \n4) The Moment That You Whisper  \nThis story centers around Kazuki's 'friend,' Kyou Sakurai, who is unceremoniously pushed by Kazuki into a portal to hell. There, Kyou meets a man who is the vessel to the Death Tunnel - responsible for sending people to hell. The man offers Kyou power to get revenge against Kazuki, but there is only one way to accomplish that…   \n  \n5) Pretentious You (oneshot)  \nA man who changes partners constantly is scolded for it by his boss. So his boss offers to be his regular lover until he finds someone to love."
  },
